{"id": 675, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得上豆瓣的都是啥样的人？", "description": "\b还是文艺青年吗？", "record_count": 5178, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183723Nq23zrJPdeKtphmB.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-12-03T10:30:32Z", "options": [{"id": 31232, "content": "豆瓣改版以后专注社交好么", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 310957}, {"id": 31744, "content": "和来这里的人差不多吧……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340271}, {"id": 33281, "content": "伪影评家\n伪剧评家\n伪书评家", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348326}, {"id": 31234, "content": "豆瓣有人吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316103}, {"id": 31235, "content": "都是小资的鸡巴软塌塌的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316103}, {"id": 31236, "content": "现在大部分人是看书籍 电影 剧集评分和一些评价吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 206045}, {"id": 34056, "content": "装作逼格很高的下半身思考的动物", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 222416}, {"id": 31241, "content": "电影没看懂，上豆瓣看看到底怎么回事的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 31242, "content": "用来看电影电视书籍的评分以及大致评价的", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 239090}, {"id": 32010, "content": "看人撕逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 341818}, {"id": 31243, "content": "看书评，看看别人的想法，再和自己的想法对比，看看自己有哪些地方需要改进", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 334551}, {"id": 33547, "content": "看影评的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 351889}, {"id": 31244, "content": "段子合集，小链接集中站?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 31248, "content": " 基本上都是穷狗逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 337546}, {"id": 31504, "content": "\n、i", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211802RsAFyg07ChqaJwXT.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338805}, {"id": 31761, "content": "看不懂东西的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340352}, {"id": 32275, "content": "找电影，找影片。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 343296}, {"id": 31252, "content": "性饥渴", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 316628}, {"id": 31253, "content": "没怎么上过豆瓣", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 106835}, {"id": 32789, "content": "一部份装的，一部分傻的，一部分真懂的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 346455}, {"id": 31254, "content": "蹲坑的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199544}, {"id": 31255, "content": "打开网站自动跳转到app", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227075}, {"id": 31256, "content": "没有钱却赖在一线城市，带着伤痕漂泊的文艺青年。", "image": null, "praise_count": 91, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313999}, {"id": 31257, "content": "看！看！看！买！！买买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 294200}, {"id": 31769, "content": "现实中空虚到爆炸，需要肯定，需要存在感", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 338553}, {"id": 33050, "content": "后来再也不去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 348075}, {"id": 31259, "content": "有趣的人在豆瓣上依然很多，用户群扩大让发现这些人变得更难了。早期积累的友邻，是上去的唯一原因。", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 45595, "content": "自恋者占多数，包括外向型自恋和内向型自恋", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 450692}, {"id": 31262, "content": "各种“去乐园”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336413}, {"id": 32032, "content": "难道不是为了抄影评？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 336918}, {"id": 31521, "content": "豆瓣是现在最直的基佬交友网站?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 49249}, {"id": 31267, "content": "反正不知道怎么样，貌似很多小清新都曾经来过后来就有了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333997}, {"id": 31270, "content": "约文艺炮的骚年", "image": null, "praise_count": 44, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 227046}, {"id": 31273, "content": "偶尔刻意彰显自己的“独特”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 323572}, {"id": 31786, "content": "骚年", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340417}, {"id": 43822, "content": "看影评的人然后决定性要不要贡献电影票时间精力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 439006}, {"id": 33843, "content": "爱读书的已绝迹，能看懂电影的也已绝迹。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 355127}, {"id": 31286, "content": "装X的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 328269}, {"id": 31543, "content": "找书评和影评的人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339078}, {"id": 31289, "content": "那些没法发到朋友圈和微博上的话，偷偷写在豆瓣上", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305810}, {"id": 34363, "content": "找配乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360530}, {"id": 31292, "content": "新一代同志交友软件?", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 67458}, {"id": 31548, "content": "穷屌丝", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 168505}, {"id": 31549, "content": "需要参考他人意见的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 339098}, {"id": 31303, "content": "看八卦看影评装逼的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335221}, {"id": 31559, "content": "豆瓣已变成豆瓣酱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303133}, {"id": 31815, "content": "没有关注过豆瓣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 340700}, {"id": 32839, "content": "要么超文艺，要么超屌丝", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 209243}, {"id": 33354, "content": "比较穷又想看上去很有范的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349985}, {"id": 34378, "content": "宅男宅女", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360552}]}